Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:16.63,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,fx,SAY WON 'T STOP LOVE YOU
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.63,0:02:19.87,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,fx,どんな小さな幸せも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.12,0:02:23.44,op-jp,,0000,0000,0000,fx,见つけ出せる気がするよ
